        <div class="fanatics-block block">
            <img class="fanatics-logo" loading="lazy" src="{{ 'fanatics-logo.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Protection. Fashion. Passion." />
            <p>Screen Skinz are Sold on Fanatics
                The official retail partner for the NFL, MLB, NBA, and NHL.</p>
                <a href="http://" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
